{"tid":2290765,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實做office工，座位有partition對公司有什麼好處?","createTime":"2020-11-18T08:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T22:47:37.000Z","uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87df0eb59e7227cf598e0752347e8395b88362af","tid":2290765,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"其實返office，要做對電腦既工<br />\n<br />\n點解有d公司座位要設有partition?<br />\n有partition，係就係有私人空間，冇人睇到你做乜<br />\n<br />\n但除左有私人空間，真係對公司百害無一利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n員工生產力嚴重下降<br />\n化妝，淘寶，聽歌，玩電話，做功課，上Facebook IG,訓教，乜都齊，偷懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開放式辨公室先令員工有工作動力<br />\n<br />\n利申: 開放式辨公室多數刻薄西工，多數唔會做"},{"pid":"ab300e55a40236590de0c82e6932f246ce1de126","tid":2290765,"uid":166733,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"要做嘅人點都會做<br />\n有得揀都唔會揀豬肉枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b887b40616e68e5d0e08a7273a40c32c95b0ce","tid":2290765,"uid":175817,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:09:57.000Z","msg":"隨便google都搵到幾個報道講open office reduces productivity"},{"pid":"3a05f08a5e2507b41045d37dc024a11b3c47591c","tid":2290765,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:01:43.000Z","msg":"都係睇你上面個管治文化嘅姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外份工係hea嘅話<br />\n就變成一個人hea同成班同事一齊hea嘅分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a413b02fa82de4ae657ee59b5b29097d5253d5c9","tid":2290765,"uid":249170,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"Neutral<br />\n<br />\n就係